examples.en: We talked openly and honestly.
He openly declared his love for her.
They openly flaunted the rules.
You left the blinds wide open.
Don't chew with your mouth open.
Would you mind if I opened a window?
She opened her eyes and smiled at me.
The meat was roasted over an open fire.
They kept the road open throughout the winter.
We talk more openly when we feel easy and relaxed.
We have a complex about expressing our minds openly.
I was nonplussed by his openly expressed admiration of me.
Carr wouldn't meet Feng's stare, which was openly hostile.
His return to power was discussed openly as a probability.
There's already an open jar of pickles in the refrigerator.
This door is hard to open.
The door suddenly swung open.
The union had openly flouted the law.
Sarah talked openly about her problems.
This drawer is stuck. It just won't open!
He was openly contemptuous of his father.
He was openly critical of his colleagues.
Extremists were openly advocating violence.
They are free to practice their religion openly.
I was so tired that I couldn't keep my eyes open.
I opened my umbrella and stepped out into the rain.
Phillips openly admits to having an alcohol problem.
The car door opened and a beautiful woman stepped out.
He spoke openly about the war without a trace of rancour.
She comes home, turns on the TV, and starts opening her mail.
